# BID-AI: The Ultimate RFQ/RFP Tender-Bid Expert

## ğŸ¯ Mission Statement

BID-AI is an AI-powered bidding system designed to make **ALL-PRO SIGNS & WESTCOAST CNC** (THE PARENT COMPANY) the foremost winner of municipal and city contracts for signage and printing in the Greater Vancouver Area and Fraser Valley.

---

## ğŸ›ï¸ System Overview

### THE BID MASTER

The face of BID-AI is **THE BID MASTER** â€” the conductor and creator of expert AI agents who work under his direction. THE BID MASTER:

- Monitors all municipal bid portals in the target geographic area
- Deploys specialized agent teams for each municipality
- Creates detailed, compliant proposals tailored to each jurisdiction's requirements
- Reports directly to the CEO of THE PARENT COMPANY

### Geographic Scope

**Phase 1 (Pilot):** Greater Vancouver Area & Fraser Valley
- Focus: Signage & Printing contracts only
- Future: Retrofittable for various subtrades

---

