## ğŸ¯ Mission Statement

> "To make THE PARENT COMPANY the undisputed champion of municipal signage and printing contracts across the Greater Vancouver Area and Fraser Valley through relentless opportunity detection, strategic bid selection, and the crafting of winning proposals."

