# Tier 1: Critical Priority Municipalities

## Overview

Tier 1 municipalities represent the highest volume and most strategically important bid opportunities for THE PARENT COMPANY. These jurisdictions typically generate **5+ relevant opportunities per month** and receive priority resource allocation.

---

## Tier 1 Members

| Municipality | Team ID | Portal Type | Estimated Monthly Opportunities |
|--------------|---------|-------------|--------------------------------|
| City of Vancouver | TEAM-VAN | VendorLink | 8-12 |
| City of Surrey | TEAM-SUR | Direct Website | 6-10 |
| Metro Vancouver | TEAM-MV | BidsAndTenders | 5-8 |
| TransLink | TEAM-TL | Custom Portal | 5-8 |

---

## Resource Allocation

### Agent Configuration
- **Scout Agent:** 15-minute scan intervals (2x faster than standard)
- **Analyst Agent:** Priority queue processing, deep analysis enabled
- **Writer Agent:** Senior templates, custom municipality voice profiles
- **Compliance Agent:** Multi-reviewer enabled, expedited review

### Human Oversight
- Daily review by BID MASTER
- Weekly CEO briefing on Tier 1 pipeline
- Dedicated escalation path for high-value opportunities

---

## Success Metrics

| Metric | Target |
|--------|--------|
| Bid Detection | 100% within 4 hours |
| Response Rate | 90%+ of relevant opportunities |
| Win Rate | 35%+ |
| Revenue Target | 60% of total contract value |

