# Materials Database Index

## Purpose

This database serves as THE BID MASTER's reference for evaluating material specifications in RFPs/RFQs. When a contract specifies materials, THE BID MASTER cross-references against:

1. **Can THE PARENT COMPANY source this material?**
2. **What is the lead time?**
3. **What is the cost basis?**
4. **Are there approved alternatives?**
5. **What supplier relationships exist?**

---

## Material Categories

### 1. Substrates (Sign Faces & Panels)

| Material | Common Specs | Typical Use | Fulfillment Status |
|----------|--------------|-------------|-------------------|
| Aluminum Composite (ACM/Dibond) | 3mm, 4mm, 6mm | Monument signs, panels | âœ… Core Capability |
| Aluminum Sheet | .040", .063", .080", .125" | Flat signs, regulatory | âœ… Core Capability |
| Acrylic (Cast/Extruded) | 3mm, 6mm, 12mm | Illuminated faces, letters | âœ… Core Capability |
| Polycarbonate (Lexan) | Various gauges | Vandal-resistant | âœ… Available |
| HDU (High Density Urethane) | 15lb, 18lb density | Carved/routed signs | âœ… Core Capability |
| PVC/Sintra | 3mm, 6mm, 12mm, 19mm | Temporary, indoor | âœ… Core Capability |
| Coroplast | 4mm, 6mm | Temporary signage | âœ… Core Capability |
| MDO Plywood | 1/2", 3/4" | Painted wood signs | âœ… Available |
| Stainless Steel | 16ga, 14ga, 11ga | Premium/architectural | âš ï¸ Specialty Order |
| Corten Steel | Various | Architectural/rustic | âš ï¸ Specialty Order |
| Bronze | Cast/sheet | Heritage/memorial | âš ï¸ Specialty Order |
| Glass | Tempered, laminated | Premium interior | âš ï¸ Subcontract |

